That's down here.

945
00:54:20,160 --> 00:54:22,083
It's not up at the North
Pole, for Pete's sake.

946
00:54:22,160 --> 00:54:25,164
Ice is ice, Dean.
This is our moment.

947
00:54:25,320 --> 00:54:28,608
