00:56:01,080 --> 00:56:04,368
Thirty bucks and I'll lend you the
magic of Guns N' Roses for 24 hours.

979
00:56:04,440 --> 00:56:08,365
Okay, Gordon Gekko, we get it.
Nice try, though.

