Hey, you know what?

997
00:56:48,480 --> 00:56:50,767
I'm not one of your endangered
critters that needs saving.

998
00:56:50,840 --> 00:56:52,444
So, thanks, anyway.

999
00:56:52,520 --> 00:56:54,727
I'm sorry, I didn't mean...

1000
00:56:54,840 --> 00:56:57,684
