holes from freezing over.

1020
00:57:51,120 --> 00:57:53,122
Yeah, you just give us the word
and we'll head out to the whales.

1021
00:57:53,200 --> 00:57:54,326
You bet.

1022
00:57:54,400 --> 00:57:57,244
