You need to see this!

1031
00:58:45,920 --> 00:58:47,524
Festive.

1032
00:58:51,120 --> 00:58:52,531
No, no, no.

1033
00:58:52,600 --> 00:58:55,922
I am doing a really good job
and I'm not leaving

