00:58:56,040 --> 00:58:59,123
just because now this is a
lead story, and you want it!

1035
00:58:59,240 --> 00:59:01,208
You want to play in
the big leagues, Jill?

1036
00:59:01,280 --> 00:59:03,123
Sometimes you have to
sit on the bench,

1037
00:59:03,240 --> 00:59:05,720
