for you at the airport.

1039
00:59:07,880 --> 00:59:09,928
I'll be keeping
your cameraman with me.

1040
00:59:12,920 --> 00:59:15,571
Good luck with
your "cat in a tree," Wes!

1041
00:59:22,640 --> 00:59:23,641
Are you Mexican?

