Jeez, look at that.
Look at that whale.

1074
01:01:25,040 --> 01:01:27,520
Don't worry about it, okay? These
things are going to work great!

1075
01:01:30,520 --> 01:01:32,090
I hope.

1076
01:01:35,200 --> 01:01:36,247
