FAA regs against that.

1129
01:04:08,000 --> 01:04:09,286
Shut it off, or we don't go.

1130
01:04:09,400 --> 01:04:11,289
It'll freeze.
This is the only way.

1131
01:04:11,400 --> 01:04:14,609
