we're going to freeze to death.

1137
01:04:55,880 --> 01:04:58,087
Seventy below?
That can't be right.

1138
01:04:59,880 --> 01:05:01,006
Feels pretty right.

1139
01:05:01,120 --> 01:05:02,645
But wait,
if we're going 100 knots,

