1557
01:36:57,760 --> 01:36:59,524
Go easy on the copy
machine because,

1558
01:36:59,600 --> 01:37:01,728
after all, it's being
held up by duct tape.

1559
01:37:07,400 --> 01:37:08,401
Is everything okay?

1560
01:37:08,480 --> 01:37:09,527
Yeah.

1561
01:37:09,600 --> 01:37:11,762
